{"tid":816220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹會係強三or弱八  同意嗎","createTime":"2018-09-12T15:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T16:07:47.000Z","uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c366b3be2bb167a58c9029c1690002ad78c805b","tid":816220,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"hi 到呂宋已經廢一半武功<br />\n前面仲有個風預早吸走南海熱量<br />\n連重新發展都唔得 最後係香港以南三百公里左右路過<br />\n預早半個星期煞有介事做準備<br />\n結果得個強三驚會冇面<br />\n所以大交合頂盡開個弱八當交差<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(一係強三一係弱八)</span><br />\n之後又繼續吹香港係福地<br />\n<br />\n結果早已預訂<br />\n學生哥學生妹好好享受弱八風假<br />\n手停口停繼續手停口停<br />\n無災無難有雨小水浸<br />\n鳩鐵繼續鳩下鳩下未爆住<br />\n<br />\n最多有傻仔玩水/行山蕩失路call飛行服務隊<br />\n然後又入個風數 講幾日打風都行山唔值得救云云 奶共網媒再老吹行山人士係港獨or黃絲點樣無腦 blablabla<br />\n<br />\n結論係打和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(香港大眾想點實際就掉番轉 事與願違呢點就成日中)"},{"pid":"9f0811e492466c14be43a745d8ae8ea8750a37c2","tid":816220,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"學生哥學生妹好好享受弱八風假<br />\n<br />\n... 星期日wo ching"},{"pid":"15ad93873f70732a590e2d09b3104b007fb63ed9","tid":816220,"uid":35776,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9f0811e492466c14be43a745d8ae8ea8750a37c2","tid":816220,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"學生哥學生妹好好享受弱八風假<br />\n<br />\n... 星期日wo ching"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"手誤<del><span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">記錯</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特殊學校個堆囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}